The datasets "flares.txt","fires.txt","terrorism_deaths.txt", and "cities.txt" are from Clauset et al. 2009. Crop indemnities ("croploss_2017.rds") are from the USDA Risk Management Agency. USGS streamflow and sediment load datasets ("streamflow.txt" and SS mg/L in "honeycreekdata.xlsx") are from USGS Water Data for the Nation, and the foreign aid dataset ("foreignaid.rds") is from the USAID Complete Development Data Library. 
